message.content: cs.AR, cs.AR because the paper deals with architecture and design of DRAM memory systems, which falls under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR). Other possible sub-categories could include cs.SY (systems and control), cs.PF (performance), cs.ET (emerging technologies), and cs.SE (software engineering) as the paper also discusses energy efficiency, latency reduction, and the development of new mechanisms for improving memory systems.
